WEBVTT

00:03:59.040 --> 00:04:03.341
It was this revolution
that started in this blank notebook

00:04:03.365 --> 00:04:05.604
30 years ago

00:04:05.628 --> 00:04:07.500
that shaped my life's work.

00:04:08.117 --> 00:04:11.405
The secret, silent
correspondence with myself.

00:04:12.656 --> 00:04:13.832
Like a gymnast,

00:04:13.856 --> 00:04:18.387
I started to move beyond
the rigidity of denial

00:04:18.411 --> 00:04:20.515
into what I've now come to call

00:04:20.539 --> 00:04:22.071
emotional agility.

00:04:26.187 --> 00:04:29.409
Life's beauty is inseparable
from its fragility.